title: Thor
synopsis: Thor fights his brother Loki in Asgard

title: Frozen
synopsis: Anna and Kristoff bravely push onward in a race to save their kingdom from winter's cold grip.

title: Hulk
synopsis: Scientist Bruce Banner's inner demons transform him in the aftermath of a catastrophic experiment

title: Shazam
synopsis: We all have a superhero inside of us, it just takes a bit of magic to bring it out.

title: Spiderman
synopsis: Student Peter Parker gets bitten by a genetically-altered spider and gains superhuman strength with the spider-like ability to cling to any surface

title: Avengers
synopsis: Nick Fury of S.H.I.E.L.D. initiates a superhero recruitment effort to defeat the unprecedented threat to Earth by building a "dream team".
casts: Tom Hiddleston;Samuel L. Jackson;Robert Downey Jr.;Chris Evans;Mark Ruffalo;Chris Hemsworth;Scarlett Johansson;Jeremy Renner

title: Eternals
synopsis: A race of immortal beings with superhuman powers who have secretly lived on Earth for thousands of years reunite to battle the evil Deviants.
casts: Angelina Jolie;Gemma Chan;Richard Madden;Kumail Nanjiani;Lauren Ridloff;Brian Tyree Henry;Salma Hayek;Lia McHugh;Don Lee;Kit Harrington

title: Batman
synopsis: Batman ventures into Gotham City's underworld when a sadistic killer leaves behind a trail of cryptic clues. As the evidence begins to lead closer to home and the scale of the perpetrator's plans become clear, he must forge new relationships, unmask the culprit and bring justice to the abuse of power and corruption that has long plagued the metropolis.
casts: Robert Pattinson;Zoë Kravitz;Paul Dano;Jeffrey Wright;John Turturro;Peter Sarsgaard;Andy Serkis;Colin Farrell

title: Avatar
synopsis: On the lush alien world of Pandora live the Na'vi, beings who appear primitive but are highly evolved. Because the planet's environment is poisonous, human/Na'vi hybrids, called Avatars, must link to human minds to allow for free movement on Pandora. Jake Sully (Sam Worthington), a paralyzed former Marine, becomes mobile again through one such Avatar and falls in love with a Na'vi woman (Zoe Saldana). As a bond with her grows, he is drawn into a battle for the survival of her world.
casts: Sam Worthington;Zoe Saldana;Stephen Lang;Michelle Rodriguez;Sigourney Weaver

title: Titanic
synopsis: James Cameron's "Titanic" is an epic and action-packed romance set against the ill-fated maiden voyage of the R.M.S. Titanic
casts: Leonardo DiCaprio;Kate Winslet;Billy Zane;Kathy Bates;Frances Fisher;Bernard Hill;Jonathan Hyde;Danny Nucci;David Warner;Bill Paxton

title: Inception
synopsis: Dom Cobb is a thief with the rare ability to enter people's dreams and steal their secrets from their subconscious.
casts: Leonardo DiCaprio;Ken Watanabe;Joseph Gordon-Levitt;Marion Cotillard;Elliot Page;Tom Hardy;Cillian Murphy;Tom Berenger;Michael Caine

title: Interstellar
synopsis: Brand sends former NASA pilot Cooper and a team of researchers through the wormhole and across the galaxy to find out which of three planets could be mankind's new home.
casts: Matthew McConaughey;Anne Hathaway;Jessica Chastain;Bill Irwin;Ellen Burstyn;Michael Caine
